fixed2free.integration

Class ColumnInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • fixed2free.integration.ColumnInfo

  • public class ColumnInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    This class serves to "decouple" the internal representation of the field meta data from the FLDL0100 format to a separate class without the AS400 classes in it. Right now the field data is the same as the java representation of the FLDL0100 format (but it does not have to remain so)
    Author:
    Eric N. Wilson
